PCI/MSI: Enable PCI_MSI_IRQ_DOMAIN support for RISC-V

Add RISC-V as an arch that supports PCI_MSI_IRQ_DOMAIN.  The related change
to generate asm/msi.h is 251a44888183 ("riscv: include generic support for
MSI irqdomains").

